ces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真人同相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都有教人整 但一對一</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983681c35fdc58403aedf52d911027a3bf31ae4c","tid":329300,"uid":28059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:03:27.000Z","msg":"想睇食譜呀今晚有無得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba1b10f1d7838319bfdf23308e43185f2fe0003","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇食譜呀今晚有無得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccdcede952ec92a65329eb1cbee506dd7cff2c9","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:14:14.000Z","msg":"Macaron馬卡龍<br />\n<br />\n材料: <br />\n蛋白30g<br />\n糖30g<br />\n糖霜40g<br />\n麵粉35g<br />\n<br />\n餡料:<br />\n黑朱古力100g<br />\n淡忌廉100g<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n做法:<br />\n1. 先將糖霜和麵粉混合至少篩兩次令粉更幼細<br />\n2. 將蛋白和蛋黃小心分開<br />\n3. 先將打蛋器調至高速，將蛋白打起至泡沫狀，逐少加入糖(分3次)，打至蛋白呈鉤狀(有紋)<br />\n4. 慢慢加入已篩過的粉，輕輕拌勻至看不到粉。<br />\n再加入2-3滴色素至混合物(蛋白/杏仁粉/糖霜)中，輕輕拌勻<br />\n5. 將已加色素的混合物放於唧袋中，唧在牛油紙上<br />\n注意:每個Macaron要分開適量位置，太近的話，焗起會粘在一起。<br />\n6. 用風筒吹乾Macaron至不粘手/放焗爐用50度烘乾20分鐘<br />\n7. 放入已預熱140度的焗爐烤烘15分鐘，取出待涼<br />\n8. 將兩件Macaron組合，在中間加入餡料即成<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n餡料做法:<br />\n黑朱古力與淡忌廉隔熱水座溶，於室溫放涼至合適硬度"},{"pid":"90cf36feb4e936dce6e3c3e07fe639cfa8eb52af","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Macaron馬卡龍<br />\n<br />\n材料: <br />\n蛋白30g<br />\n糖30g<br />\n糖霜40g<br />\n麵粉35g<br />\n<br />\n餡料:<br />\n黑朱古力100g<br />\n淡忌廉100g<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n做法:<br />\n1. 先將糖霜和麵粉混合至少篩兩次令粉更幼細<br />\n2. 將蛋白和蛋黃小心分開<br />\n3. 先將打蛋器調至高速，將蛋白打起至泡沫狀，逐少加入糖(分3次)，打至蛋白呈鉤狀(有紋)<br />\n4. 慢慢加入已篩過的粉，輕輕拌勻至看不到粉。<br />\n再加入2-3滴色素至混合物(蛋白/杏仁粉/糖霜)中，輕輕拌勻<br />\n5. 將已加色素的混合物放於唧袋中，唧在牛油紙上<br />\n注意:每個Macaron要分開適量位置，太近的話，焗起會粘在一起。<br />\n6. 用風筒吹乾Macaron至不粘手/放焗爐用50度烘乾20分鐘<br />\n7. 放入已預熱140度的焗爐烤烘15分鐘，取出待涼<br />\n8. 將兩件Macaron組合，在中間加入餡料即成<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n餡料做法:<br />\n黑朱古力與淡忌廉隔熱水座溶，於室溫放涼至合適硬度</blockquote><br />\n4.  係(蛋白/麵粉/糖霜)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59e20d8e6d564a87b92590bf0f656bf94430627","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/012415_a7e5b5ce7212ef8b1ee59b2a2d89491e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F012415_a7e5b5ce7212ef8b1ee59b2a2d89491e.jpg&h=51168a98&s={SIZE}\" />篩粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/012434_ceabd0c78ade6700bfd97a2b01971b40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F012434_ceabd0c78ade6700bfd97a2b01971b40.jpg&h=1e96603b&s={SIZE}\" />篩左2次既粉 好幼細"},{"pid":"b6eb70ae96fc231208c4e9f61ea237d276aca32d","tid":329300,"uid":126947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:27:59.000Z","msg":"次次係屋企整都失敗<br />\n但出去上堂又整到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c18b823469ed8851114a249e9ec3577983f8c79","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次係屋企整都失敗<br />\n但出去上堂又整到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出去學完返到屋企又整唔番？"},{"pid":"22f80639af5159748dc37998a835e5e4e2a7fa77","tid":329300,"uid":96303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T18:11:30.000Z","msg":"請問麵粉同杏仁粉食落下分別大唔大?"},{"pid":"ab8f22345aa666e365856715f18d280788abadd3","tid":329300,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟痴口定唔痴口嘅先正宗<br />\n藍帶教嘅就痴口不過試過某個法國產嘅係唔痴<br />\n依家食到嘅都好似無以前紅嗰排嗰啲咁痴"},{"pid":"351a692708cc2f430ea5095fc52364bb11a4e5bd","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問麵粉同杏仁粉食落下分別大唔大?</blockquote><br />\n我自己岩岩試食<br />\n用麵粉就無左陣杏仁味同無咁煙un<br />\n口感比唔上用杏仁粉 <br />\n大家練習完可以用返杏仁粉整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4f2c9bc699f1e898b9ce96076e617e69ed15e0","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:41:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟痴口定唔痴口嘅先正宗<br />\n藍帶教嘅就痴口不過試過某個法國產嘅係唔痴<br />\n依家食到嘅都好似無以前紅嗰排嗰啲咁痴</blockquote><br />\n痴口先正宗 連藍帶教既都痴口你就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為出面太多人整到鬼五馬六<br />\n我去放題食既 一咬成口粉添"},{"pid":"fc494d44a8a0ff7804b1e93554e1d81e0caf2b03","tid":329300,"uid":21426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"我幾年前去過cookingsiulam度學整<br />\n上堂嗰陣整得好靚<br />\n但返屋企整幾次都痴底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無話咩原因會導致痴底？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af1e99899f4300f99178ae396002fbcfc0ba65f","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T06:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我幾年前去過cookingsiulam度學整<br />\n上堂嗰陣整得好靚<br />\n但返屋企整幾次都痴底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無話咩原因會導致痴底？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為未熟呀<br />\n熟左就一野meet到出黎<br />\n可以買不沾布整 更加易脫"},{"pid":"f854620a908c212e4a03887caf0d8e6463e51622","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T06:18