/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面放左食譜 <br />\n有咩唔明再問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25fc813ea1f1ee236207750e9dcbd276ff6701d","tid":329300,"uid":40139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T07:58:27.000Z","msg":"想問蛋白30g大概要用幾多隻蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想整但係次次都驚整整下唔夠蛋用"},{"pid":"8019e0e47416ccde158c83c6532d11bb0f510526","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T08:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問蛋白30g大概要用幾多隻蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想整但係次次都驚整整下唔夠蛋用</blockquote><br />\n買定多啲蛋咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n30g一隻大蛋夠晒"},{"pid":"9f28171d28777e1f859be5352c31a214597eeee3","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/183542_3a162d4280cfa93caee11598b0f06c97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F183542_3a162d4280cfa93caee11598b0f06c97.jpg&h=82974382&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b17fc16c3fef62984dc0c739fa34a8b9f121497","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/184116_7f262d1b5a05cfe319d96dd5679fdc6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F184116_7f262d1b5a05cfe319d96dd5679fdc6a.jpg&h=2db5116e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"855ede7f34e2989de25aaaf14b95df72ed853872","tid":329300,"uid":127423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/183542_3a162d4280cfa93caee11598b0f06c97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F183542_3a162d4280cfa93caee11598b0f06c97.jpg&h=82974382&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n超勁"},{"pid":"263372aa217d1783014094cc8951bcb4a9ba352e","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/183542_3a162d4280cfa93caee11598b0f06c97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F183542_3a162d4280cfa93caee11598b0f06c97.jpg&h=82974382&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n超勁</blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade1053e0923cea59dbbdc8e40cc3afe6ff463f3","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/103811_7152d7ae78963368054a2547e66b6a33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F103811_7152d7ae78963368054a2547e66b6a33.jpg&h=6fb15937&s={SIZE}\" />當日焗蛋黃哥都幾緊張<br />\n因為第一次整麵粉版馬卡龍<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/103852_924023d607c84a64b6bf1c4d0c342cbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F103852_924023d607c84a64b6bf1c4d0c342cbe.jpg&h=90541060&s={SIZE}\" />好在都出到裙邊"},{"pid":"ba3606df5a746e07657e4f6687c23fa3fa76b76a","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:58:02.000Z","msg":"Macaron馬卡龍<br />\n<br />\n材料: <br />\n蛋白30g<br />\n糖30g<br />\n糖霜40g<br />\n麵粉35g<br />\n<br />\n餡料:<br />\n黑朱古力100g<br />\n淡忌廉100g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做法:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/105234_a3aa826e2b965c121eb168238fec2170.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F105234_a3aa826e2b965c121eb168238fec2170.jpg&h=f7470b59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/105245_8ad098fee3bda85d21229dfb99db05bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F105245_8ad098fee3bda85d21229dfb99db05bc.jpg&h=d685f3b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/105256_c99ec6ddcb4ef7a8284c9fe1f62b14a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F105256_c99ec6ddcb4ef7a8284c9fe1f62b14a7.jpg&h=f0755e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/105309_b6d41237e009e07e59bc0e10162536c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F105309_b6d41237e009e07e59bc0e10162536c8.jpg&h=392f4eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5. 再加入2-3滴色素至混合物(麵粉/糖霜/蛋白)，輕輕拌勻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/105724_2841066f26235f01c9a7e134af5e1b93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F105724_2841066f26235f01c9a7e134af5e1b93.jpg&h=471bc9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7.  放焗爐用50度烘乾20分鐘<br />\n8. 放入已預熱140度的焗爐烤烘15分鐘，取出待涼<br />\n9. 將兩件Macaron組合，在中間加入餡料即成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n餡料做法:<br />\n黑朱古力與淡忌廉隔熱水座溶，於室溫放涼至合適硬度"},{"pid":"73ba731ecbdf2d328e0c7cc9c2966e23ef242592","tid":329300,"uid":128509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T10:59:48.000Z","msg":"好靚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次整都fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n焗時用上下火？"},{"pid":"a486a936a823aafdb0e4169230126731b59e2ef4","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好靚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次整都fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n焗時用上下火？</blockquote><br />\n無錯 上下火<br />\n我用上下發熱管+旋轉 既模式"},{"pid":"1833ec9563d1b44c2f7557019c8c22d6a931d500","tid":329300,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:20:34.000Z","msg":"整得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打識唔識整Brownie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a06ceec5db7c303cde80b270afae65d3ba25127","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打識唔識整Brownie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識呀 我整開有士多啤梨版本<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係上網睇 好易整"},{"pid":"3b24574f10deeeff25778498d7becb7a93541599","tid":329300,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:17:44.000Z","msg":"雖然我好憎食馬卡龍亦未曾食過好食的，但樓主又整得幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a40253eae713e476711ae5180e5931501bea54b","tid":329300,"uid":128531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然我好憎食馬卡龍亦未曾食過好食的，但樓主又整得幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實整得好係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我明既 因為我係出面都無食過好食既<br />\n你有興趣可以請你食啲<br />\n令你改變個睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4898f0f1826216fc266b9f53ebe8ecfa397460","tid":329300,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092eb7d84a9db0401b53